        "subject": "LU-2133 lnet: wrong peer state reported",
        "message": "LU-2133 lnet: wrong peer state reported\n\nWhen peer health is not enabled, peer state as shown in\n/proc/sys/lnet/peers and by IOC_LIBCFS_DEBUG_PEER should be \"NA\".\nOtherwise wrong states could be shown because the peer aliveness time\nstamps are not refreshed when peer health is disabled.\n\nSigned-off-by: Isaac Huang <he.huang@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I762c16853a824debd0de84cbf6b1863825ab608e\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
